descriptionNullable:
This dataset collects images of Portuguese traffic signs in both regular and unfavorable conditions, which include:
- Discoloration
- Paint peeling off;
- Scratches;
- Being bent;
- Rust;
- Graffiti;
- Stickers;
- Partial Occlusion;
- Design flaws;
- Reflections;
- Blurring;
- And other types of deterioration.

The pictures were collected with the intent of being used for traffic sign detection and classification problems.

